Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Documentary papyrus
Description: Documentary papyrus with remains of six lines originating from two different hands (the same handwriting was used in lines 1, 5, 6). A possible mention of fractions in lines 5 and 6 reminds one of calculations, though their exact nature eludes us.
